       Craken looks to the vastness of the African Plains. He is amazed such 
a beautiful Country could exsist, although his world of water will always 
remain his most favorite of places.
       "This is Craken. I am a Predacon, and wish to join my fellow 
Predacons. My coordinates are 6578 South West." He sent a broad cast on all 
Predacon frequences, hoping that someone would show up, or answer back.

--part1_44.b4e1972.27b9c482_boundary
